00:02:09,462 --> 00:02:12,829
This morning, at exactly 5:18 a. m...

7
00:02:13,266 --> 00:02:16,497
...here at ICON's Institute
for Data Analysis...

8
00:02:17,203 --> 00:02:20,195
...we installed the final module...

9
00:02:20,406 --> 00:02:24,172
