00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:44,021
And music.

19
00:03:46,192 --> 00:03:48,558
Hello, Maria.

20
00:03:52,732 --> 00:03:55,394
I brought you some strawberries.

21
00:03:55,935 --> 00:03:58,199
Aren't they wonderful?

22
00:03:59,305 --> 00:04:01,205
They're very nice.

23
00:04:07,146 --> 00:04:08,443
What's the matter, Maria?

24
00:04:09,649 --> 00:04:11,207
Nothing.

25
00:04:14,787 --> 00:04:17,620
