when you're gone?

26
00:04:18,591 --> 00:04:20,252
Oh, come on.

27
00:04:20,460 --> 00:04:23,623
Now, you know this thing runs itself.

28
00:04:23,796 --> 00:04:27,357
I'm gonna put its instructions in
for the next three months.

29
00:04:50,723 --> 00:04:53,590
Tell Mrs. Harris I'll be in the lab, Maria.

30
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:36,395
This is ridiculous.

31
00:05:36,602 --> 00:05:40,698
- What?
- I said, this is ridiculous.

32
00:05:41,407 --> 00:05:42,999
