33
00:05:44,210 --> 00:05:47,407
- Good as new, almost.
- I'm talking about your moving out.

34
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:50,674
- You don't want me to go?
- This is your home. It seems...

35
00:05:50,917 --> 00:05:53,215
