41
00:06:11,604 --> 00:06:15,131
But 73 percent of all couples who
separate are happy after one year.

42
00:06:15,308 --> 00:06:18,141
- And 85 percent after two years.
- For God's sakes.

43
00:06:18,311 --> 00:06:20,575
What's the matter, do I bother you?
I bore you, perhaps?

44
00:06:20,747 --> 00:06:23,443
You'd rather I had a screaming fit.

45
00:06:23,883 --> 00:06:25,874
Good God, yes!

46
00:06:29,489 --> 00:06:32,356
Yes, more wreckage.

47
00:06:33,292 --> 00:06:36,750
Trouble is, you see, we...
We have different visions of the world.

48
00:06:38,364 --> 00:06:39,888
You find me boring.

49
00:06:40,099 --> 00:06:43,262
I find myself quite interesting, really.

50
00:06:47,373 --> 00:06:49,739
You don't bore me, Alex.

51
00:06:50,042 --> 00:06:51,270
I'm frightened for you.

52
00:06:51,911 --> 00:06:56,871
You and your pompous ICON buddies
inside that mountainside.

53
00:06:58,384 --> 00:07:03,253
It's the whole dehumanizing
Proteus madness.

54
00:07:03,456 --> 00:07:05,185
Dehumanizing?

