Gabler.

72
00:08:58,304 --> 00:08:59,737
Oh, hi, Alex.

73
00:09:00,706 --> 00:09:03,869
Yeah, well, this earthquake retrieval
program is very far out.

74
00:09:05,077 --> 00:09:08,376
