92
00:11:02,194 --> 00:11:04,458
- You know Dr. Petrosian, don't you?
- Doctor.

93
00:11:04,764 --> 00:11:08,461
- Mr. Mokri. Mr. Cameron.
- Nice to meet you, sir.

94
00:11:11,103 --> 00:11:13,128
So we're going to see it, Alex...

95
00:11:13,305 --> 00:11:15,899
...at last, huh?
- Yes, you are.

96
00:11:17,843 --> 00:11:19,708
That is correct, Mr. Cameron.

97
00:11:20,346 --> 00:11:24,476
Proteus Four is now
a functioning system.

98
00:11:25,084 --> 00:11:29,145
We've performed over 6000 tests
debugging it.

99
00:11:31,257 --> 00:11:35,091
Dr. Alex, if this is not a computer
in the usual sense...

100
00:11:35,528 --> 00:11:36,859
...what is it?

101
00:11:37,029 --> 00:11:40,396
Well, it's the first
true synthetic cortex.

102
00:11:40,566 --> 00:11:43,194
A self-programming, goal-oriented...

103
