- Why not? We hope so.

134
00:13:24,203 --> 00:13:27,604
Are the proper steps being taken
to patent this?

135
00:13:27,940 --> 00:13:29,601
I have no idea.

136
00:13:30,476 --> 00:13:32,876
Alex, I'd like to hear it speak.

137
00:13:33,045 --> 00:13:35,070
