Amy, you must not behave this way.

184
00:16:59,651 --> 00:17:02,211
- Amy, get out of this car!
- Good morning, Mrs. Talbert.

185
00:17:02,388 --> 00:17:05,016
Dr. Harris, she won't get out
of the car.

186
00:17:07,626 --> 00:17:09,150
Hello, Amy.

187
00:17:09,895 --> 00:17:11,795
Come on in.

188
00:17:13,399 --> 00:17:15,663
Come on. I have something
to show you.

189
00:17:22,708 --> 00:17:26,235
- I'll see you in about an hour.
- Fine. Thank you, doctor.

190
