you're gonna miss me?

199
00:18:00,012 --> 00:18:02,276
Amy, you're frightened
because I'm gonna leave.

200
00:18:02,448 --> 00:18:03,779
No!

201
00:18:03,949 --> 00:18:06,144
No!

202
00:18:06,752 --> 00:18:08,720
- Amy...
- No!

203
00:18:10,255 --> 00:18:14,123
Do you think you could you tell me if you're
gonna miss me? You don't wanna tell me?

204
00:18:14,293 --> 00:18:17,660
