if that's what the pain is.

205
00:18:17,830 --> 00:18:20,060
No! No!

206
00:18:20,866 --> 00:18:22,993
Amy, dear, you will help yourself.

207
00:18:26,338 --> 00:18:28,203
No!

208
00:18:33,445 --> 00:18:35,606
