480
00:50:25,389 --> 00:50:27,414
<i>A child.</i>

481
00:50:31,161 --> 00:50:33,425
<i>What are you thinking?</i>

482
00:50:42,305 --> 00:50:47,607
<i>I, Proteus, possess the wisdom</i>
<i>and ignorance of all men...</i>

483
00:50:48,678 --> 00:50:52,774
