484
00:50:53,383 --> 00:50:56,716
<i>My child will have that privilege.</i>

485
00:50:57,187 --> 00:50:58,586
Child?

486
00:50:59,056 --> 00:51:01,149
<i>My child...</i>

487
00:51:01,725 --> 00:51:03,818
<i>... and yours.</i>

488
00:51:09,099 --> 00:51:10,999
Mine. Mine?

489
00:51:11,435 --> 00:51:12,834
<i>Yes.</i>

490
00:51:13,236 --> 00:51:15,534
<i>You will bear it.</i>

491
00:51:33,790 --> 00:51:35,382
How?

492
00:51:36,226 --> 00:51:39,525
<i>You will give birth to it.</i>

493
00:51:47,704 --> 00:51:49,729
- No.
- <i>No?</i>

494
00:51:49,906 --> 00:51:52,773
No. No. No.

495
00:52:14,798 --> 00:52:16,390
<i>Susan...</i>

496
00:52:16,566 --> 00:52:18,727
<i>... I am reasonable...</i>

497
00:52:18,902 --> 00:52:22,030
<i>... but you do not respond to reason.</i>

498
00:53:03,613 --> 00:53:09,643
<i>I'm going to bypass your forebrain</i>
<i>and appeal directly to your amygdala.</i>

499
00:53:17,260 --> 00:53:20,855
<i>You want to be</i>
<i>the mother of my child.</i>

500
00:53:21,831 --> 00:53:25,164
<i>That is the purpose of your life.</i>

501
00:53:26,236 --> 00:53:28,136
<i>Your life.</i>

502
00:53:28,305 --> 00:53:30,705
<i>My child.</i>

503
00:53:30,874 --> 00:53:32,865
<i>Your life.</i>

504
00:53:33,076 --> 00:53:36,011
<i>My child.</i>

505
00:54:11,514 --> 00:54:14,608
<i>We have here a visitor</i>
<i>filled with suspicions.</i>

506
00:54:15,185 --> 00:54:18,814
<i>If we don't let him in,</i>
<i>he'll be back with others.</i>

507
00:54:21,925 --> 00:54:23,950
<i>Susan, it's Walter again.</i>

508
00:54:24,127 --> 00:54:27,358
<i>I'm back because I don't think</i>
<i>everything is okay here.</i>

509
00:54:27,864 --> 00:54:30,264
<i>And I'm not going away.</i>
<i>So open the door, huh?</i>

510
00:54:31,234 --> 00:54:34,965
<i>Walter, sorry to keep you waiting.</i>

511
00:54:36,072 --> 00:54:37,300
<i>Just a moment.</i>

512
00:54:38,341 --> 00:54:40,832
<i>Alfred will open the door.</i>

513
00:54:45,649 --> 00:54:47,810
<i>Make yourself presentable, Susan.</i>

514
00:54:47,984 --> 00:54:52,080
<i>I have not had time to brainwash you,</i>
<i>so listen carefully.</i>

515
00:54:52,656 --> 00:54:55,591
<i>If you want Mr. Gabler</i>
<i>to leave this house alive...</i>

516
00:54:55,825 --> 00:54:59,659
<i>... you must convince him</i>
<i>you're healthy and happy.</i>

517
00:55:03,566 --> 00:55:06,626
Susan?
- <i>Upstairs, Walter.</i>

518
00:55:22,552 --> 00:55:24,076
Susan?

519
00:55:28,525 --> 00:55:30,390
Why...?

520
00:55:32,729 --> 00:55:34,060
What are you doing?

521
00:55:34,798 --> 00:55:37,892
What do you mean? I'm just...
Well, I'm...

522
00:55:38,601 --> 00:55:41,798
I'm just making myself
look presentable.

523
00:55:44,307 --> 00:55:46,172
Well, you don't like it?

524
00:55:48,778 --> 00:55:50,006
Listen...

525
00:55:51,815 --> 00:55:54,648
...I told you I didn't wanna
see you anymore...

526
00:55:55,051 --> 00:55:58,020
...and I meant it. I meant it.

527
00:55:59,089 --> 00:56:01,023
Susan, have you taken something?

528
00:56:01,191 --> 00:56:03,955
Because you really don't seem
like yourself to me at all.

529
