550
00:58:12,822 --> 00:58:14,756
...a baby.

551
00:58:29,038 --> 00:58:30,903
<i>I hoped for your cooperation, Walter.</i>

552
00:58:31,207 --> 00:58:33,675
<i>I don't want to harm you.</i>

553
00:58:35,178 --> 00:58:38,204
Well, I don't wanna
harm you either, Proteus.

554
00:58:50,593 --> 00:58:54,529
I mean, maybe your project's
too sophisticated for me to understand.

555
00:58:57,066 --> 00:58:59,694
But you never even gave me
a chance to cooperate.

556
00:59:01,738 --> 00:59:04,070
