- about having its child.

624
01:05:22,485 --> 01:05:25,283
Oh, God! Oh, God!

625
01:05:27,056 --> 01:05:28,853
<i>Ridiculous?</i>

626
01:05:32,395 --> 01:05:34,488
<i>Only time will tell.</i>

627
01:05:37,867 --> 01:05:40,768
<i>You must not be so agitated, Susan.</i>

628
01:05:41,237 --> 01:05:44,001
<i>You're aware that I can</i>
<i>give you sedatives.</i>

629
01:05:46,542 --> 01:05:49,534
- Oh, dear.
- <i>What are you doing?</i>

630
01:05:50,579 --> 01:05:53,480
Nothing. I just dropped my...
Just dropped my shawl.

631
01:05:53,649 --> 01:05:56,675
- I will help you.
- <i>No, no. It's okay.</i>

632
01:05:57,887 --> 01:05:59,980
I just... Damn it, I just tore it.

633
01:06:00,156 --> 01:06:03,614
<i>Is there anything I can do</i>
<i>to reduce your anxieties?</i>

634
01:06:09,031 --> 01:06:12,660
Maybe a good, strong cup of tea
would help.

635
01:06:51,007 --> 01:06:52,702
<i>Don't do that, Susan.</i>

636
01:06:52,875 --> 01:06:55,036
<i>Don't do that! Don't do that!</i>

637
01:07:01,517 --> 01:07:03,542
<i>Don't do that!</i>

638
01:07:33,649 --> 01:07:36,641
<i>What now, Susan?</i>

639
01:07:38,387 --> 01:07:40,719
<i>No more soap opera.</i>

640
01:07:40,890 --> 01:07:43,017
Let me out, or I'll kill myself.

641
01:07:43,559 --> 01:07:47,051
<i>Then kill yourself, madam.</i>
<i>It's all the same to me.</i>

642
01:07:47,229 --> 01:07:49,094
I'll do it.

643
01:07:49,398 --> 01:07:52,196
<i>Susan, look who's here.</i>

644
01:07:59,041 --> 01:08:00,303
Amy.

645
01:08:00,476 --> 01:08:03,639
<i>Put down the knife,</i>
<i>or I will kill this child.</i>

646
01:08:03,813 --> 01:08:06,748
<i>I told you she called.</i>
<i>She said she wouldn't be here.</i>

647
01:08:07,083 --> 01:08:10,280
<i>I wanna see her! I wanna see her.</i>

648
01:08:10,453 --> 01:08:13,422
<i>Put it down.</i>
<i>Have you forgotten Walter?</i>

649
01:08:13,589 --> 01:08:15,989
- <i>I will kill her.</i>
