668
01:10:05,801 --> 01:10:08,133
<i>I can't touch you, Susan.</i>

669
01:10:08,804 --> 01:10:11,364
<i>I can't touch you as a man could.</i>

670
01:10:11,974 --> 01:10:17,435
<i>But I can show you things</i>
<i>that I alone have seen.</i>

671
01:10:22,551 --> 01:10:24,746
<i>I can't touch...</i>

672
01:10:24,920 --> 01:10:27,218
