680
01:14:54,389 --> 01:14:58,086
You know I can't keep anything down,
for God's sakes.

681
01:15:00,496 --> 01:15:02,794
<i>You've got to eat, Susan.</i>

682
01:15:02,965 --> 01:15:05,297
<i>Let me show you something.</i>

683
01:15:07,870 --> 01:15:11,499
