685
01:15:23,452 --> 01:15:25,477
It's so developed.

686
01:15:33,028 --> 01:15:35,792
<i>What is, is natural.</i>

687
01:15:36,331 --> 01:15:40,358
<i>The fetus is now growing</i>
<i>at nine times the normal rate.</i>

688
01:15:40,569 --> 01:15:42,230
<i>In 28 days...</i>

689
01:15:42,404 --> 01:15:46,101
<i>... you will give birth</i>
<i>to a full-term infant.</i>

690
01:15:48,210 --> 01:15:52,647
<i>From your womb, it will be transferred</i>
<i>directly to this incubator.</i>

691
01:15:52,848 --> 01:15:56,784
- And how long will it stay there?
- <i>Until it's ready</i>.

692
01:15:56,952 --> 01:16:01,912
<i>In there, its brain will be fed the formal</i>
<i>structures of my own intelligence.</i>

693
01:16:02,090 --> 01:16:06,288
<i>In there, it will grow and grow.</i>

694
01:16:15,904 --> 01:16:17,804
<i>Time is short.</i>

