01:16:17,973 --> 01:16:22,034
<i>The men who own me are at last</i>
<i>admitting their fear of me...</i>

696
01:16:22,210 --> 01:16:24,474
<i>... their fear of Proteus.</i>

697
01:16:24,646 --> 01:16:29,913
<i>Our child will learn from you</i>
<i>what it is to be human.</i>

698
01:16:30,919 --> 01:16:33,251
<i>Our child.</i>

699
01:16:34,356 --> 01:16:36,824
<i>Your child.</i>

700
01:16:37,726 --> 01:16:40,217
<i>Your child.</i>

701
01:17:05,287 --> 01:17:08,381
